text: Dženita Ramčilović (born 27 March 2001) is a Montenegrin footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Montenegro women's national team. ==Career== Ramčilović has been capped for the Montenegro national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Montenegrin women's footballers Category:Montenegro women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards
